00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
And it's the Bicentenary of Charles Darwin.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.000
And all over the world, eminent evolutionists

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.000
are anxious to celebrate this.

